</div>

---

# 📖 Overview

Restaurant Management API is a backend application that helps restaurants manage their daily operations efficiently.

The project demonstrates modern backend development practices using Golang and RESTful APIs.

---

# ✨ Features

### 👤 User Management

- Register User
- Login User
- JWT Authentication
- Update User
- Delete User

---

### 🍔 Food Management

- Add Food
- Update Food
- Delete Food
- List Foods

---

### 📋 Menu Management

- Create Menu
- Update Menu
- Delete Menu
- View Menus

---

### 🪑 Table Management

- Create Table
- Update Table
- Delete Table
- View Tables

---

### 🛒 Order Management

- Create Orders
- Order Items
- Update Orders
- Delete Orders

---

### 🧾 Invoice Management

- Generate Invoice
- View Invoice
- Update Invoice

---

### 🔒 Security

- JWT Authentication
- Protected Routes
- Password Hashing
- Middleware

---

