# 📂 Project Structure

```text
restaurant-management/

├── controllers/
│
├── databases/
│
├── helpers/
│
├── middleware/
│
├── models/
│
├── routes/
│
├── .gitignore
├── go.mod
├── go.sum
└── main.go
```

---

# 🏗 System Architecture

```text
                    Client
                       │
                 HTTP Request
                       │
                Gin HTTP Router
                       │
                 Authentication
                 Middleware Layer
                       │
                  Controllers
                       │
                    Models
                       │
                     GORM
                       │
                    MySQL
```

---

# 🚀 Getting Started

## Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/restaurant-management-api.git
```

Move into project

```bash
cd restaurant-management-api
```

Install dependencies

```bash
go mod tidy
```

Run project

```bash
go run main.go
```

---

# 🔐 Authentication

All protected APIs require

```
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
```

